<li><a href="http://divinarecords.com/articles.htm" class="external text" title="http://divinarecords.com/articles.htm" rel="nofollow">Articles on Callas</a> In depth articles discussing Callas's recorded legacy by Dr. Robert E. Seletsky and Milan Petkovic.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.operadis-opera-discography.org.uk/CLSICALL.HTM" class="external text" title="http://www.operadis-opera-discography.org.uk/CLSICALL.HTM" rel="nofollow">Discography</a> (Capon's Lists of Opera Recordings)</li>
