<li><a href="http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&amp;GRid=3016" class="external text" title="http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&amp;GRid=3016" rel="nofollow">Maria Callas</a> at <a href="/wiki/Find_A_Grave" title="Find A Grave">Find A Grave</a></li>
