<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EBDeRmXLS6s" class="external text" title="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EBDeRmXLS6s" rel="nofollow">Maria Callas in an excerpt from <i>Tosca</i></a> (1956).</li>
</ul>
